metadata.author: NIPPON WANDERING TV
metadata.description: Relaxing walk in Tokyo Akihabara at night. Akihabara is a popular sightseeing spot in Tokyo and it's crowded with otaku geeks and tourists everyday. Enjoy the ambience of Akihabara through my video.
metadata.title: The Largest Electric Town In Tokyo - 4K Walking Tour
